## Verification Plan

### Browser Verification
1. Run the dev frontend (`cd frontend && npm run dev -- --host`) and backend (`cd backend && php artisan serve --port=8085`), which are already running.
2. Navigate to the Search page (`/search`) and visually inspect:
   - Mapped procedures display a green "Mapped" badge and have a more pronounced card style.
   - The "Mapped Only" toggle filters the list to show only mapped procedures.
   - The speciality dropdown filters by speciality and the procedure count updates accordingly.
   - Combining both filters works correctly.
